      %h1 Take Away
      %ul
        %li
          Insurance is a form of risk management that allows an insured entity (individual/corporation)
          to protect itself and transfer away its risks to the insurer.
        %li
          The insured has to pay a premium in order to get compensated in case of a loss.
        %li Premium amounts vary depending on the insured’s profile.
        %li
          There are two broad categories of life insurance policies i.e. protection policies
          and investment policies
